---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Beli vs Sewa Peralatan - Panduan 2026',
  slug: 'beli-vs-sewa-peralatan-panduan-2026',
  excerpt: 'Beli vs sewa peralatan? Panduan lengkap untuk keputusan 2026. Beli dengan 0% deposit untuk ownership penuh. Sewa untuk fleksibiliti. Bank tawarkan 90% untuk beli sahaja. Ing Heng tawarkan 100% pinjaman.',
  date: '2026-01-01',
  author: 'Pasukan Ing Heng Credit',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Peralatan',
  image: '/images/blog/excavator-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['beli vs sewa peralatan', 'pembiayaan peralatan', 'hire purchase', 'leasing', '0% deposit'];
const breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Utama', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/ms/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Peralatan</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min bacaan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Beli vs Sewa - Keputusan Penting</h2>

      <p>Pilihan antara beli dan sewa peralatan adalah keputusan penting untuk perniagaan anda. Setiap pilihan mempunyai kelebihan dan kekurangan.</p>

      <p>Panduan ini akan membantu anda membuat keputusan yang tepat untuk situasi perniagaan anda.</p>

      <h2>Beli Peralatan - Ownership Penuh</h2>

      <p>Membeli peralatan memberikan anda ownership penuh:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Ownership:</strong> Milik penuh selepas bayar</li>
        <li><strong>Asset:</strong> Tambah nilai perniagaan</li>
        <li><strong>Fleksibel:</strong> Guna macam mana pun</li>
        <li><strong>Resale:</strong> Boleh jual kemudian</li>
        <li><strong>Depresiasi:</strong> Boleh claim tax</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Tetapi membeli memerlukan deposit besar di muka.</p>

      <h2>Sewa Peralatan - Fleksibiliti</h2>

      <p>Menyewa peralatan memberikan fleksibiliti:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fleksibel:</strong> Boleh tukar peralatan</li>
        <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Selalunya termasuk</li>
        <li><strong>Upgrade:</strong> Boleh upgrade model baharu</li>
        <li><strong>Cash flow:</strong> Deposit kecil</li>
        <li><strong>Risiko:</strong> Kurang risiko kepunyaan</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Tetapi sewa lebih mahal jangka panjang dan tiada ownership.</p>

      <h2>Jadual Perbandingan</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left;">Ciri-ciri</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Sewa</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Beli (Bank)</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Beli (Ing Heng)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Deposit</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Kecil</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9fafb;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Ownership</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #dc2626;">Tidak</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #16a34a;">Ya</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #16a34a;"><strong>Ya</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Pembiayaan</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">-</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">90%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>100%</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Bila Pilih Beli?</h2>

      <p>Pilih beli jika:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Penggunaan tinggi:</strong> Guna setiap hari</li>
        <li><strong>Jangka panjang:</strong> Perlukan 5+ tahun</li>
        <li><strong>Asset value:</strong> Mahu bina nilai perniagaan</li>
        <li><strong>Kustomisasi:</strong> Perlukan modify peralatan</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Dengan 0% deposit dari Ing Heng, beli jadi lebih mudah!</p>

      <h2>Bila Pilih Sewa?</h2>

      <p>Pilih sewa jika:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Penggunaan rendah:</strong> Guna kadang-kadang</li>
        <li><strong>Jangka pendek:</strong> Perlukan kurang 2 tahun</li>
        <li><strong>Testing:</strong> Nak cuba dulu</li>
        <li><strong>Upgrade:</strong> Nak tukar model baharu</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contoh Sebenar</h2>

      <p><strong>Equipment:</strong> Forklift RM20,000</p>

      <p><strong>Sewa (2 tahun):</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit: RM2,000</li>
        <li>Monthly: RM1,000</li>
        <li>Total: RM26,000</li>
        <li>Ownership: Tidak</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Beli dengan Ing Heng (0% deposit):</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit: RM0</li>
        <li>Monthly: RM800 (5 tahun)</li>
        <li>Total: RM48,000</li>
        <li>Ownership: Ya</li>
        <li>Asset value: RM10,000 (resale)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Hubungi Kami</h2>

      <p>Pergi beli atau sewa? Kami boleh bantu buat keputusan. Dapatkan konsultasi percuma hari ini.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Beli vs Sewa? Konsultasi Percuma</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">WhatsApp kami untuk nasihat. Dapatkan 0% deposit jika pilih beli.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Hubungi:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Konsultasi Percuma" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
